    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Intentionally loading with additional weight; with regard to fibers and textiles, the addition of a substance to increase the weight or bulk of the fibers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
